{"tid":2456043,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"楊潤雄稱會免費向中小學派發國情讀本《我的家在中國》共48本書","createTime":"2021-03-21T15:09:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T01:46:06.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"5ee11bb1e33203856aac38fee062481a073131b0","tid":2456043,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T15:09:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581761-20210321.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581761-20210321.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Hu0SY4Cx1oodln7cCHpxbRAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=b1e0487f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581761-20210321.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=9beb550a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581761-20210321.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n教育局局長楊潤雄接受內地中新社訪問表示，將會免費向全港中小學派發國情讀本《我的家在中國》，作為教輔材料。讀本在內地發行，有繁體版本，涵蓋6個範疇，包括城市、道路、山河等一共48本書。<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄表示，會透過課程及不同科目，包括中文，中國歷史或地理科，傳揚重要價值觀，亦會透過《憲法》、《基本法》及國家安全教育的教材，輔助教學，當局會改善學校課程、提供教材指引、開展課外活動等，培養學生的國家觀念和身份認同，他認為國家過去經歷很多困難，需要一代又一代的愛國人士努力。"},{"pid":"ae0bd65e4e628dc90886138c2b172952665af410","tid":2456043,"uid":237487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T15:11:33.000Z","msg":"快啲去拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拎撚哂佢"},{"pid":"83bff9feb46031cf1513c00acea29ab8bbb5290b","tid":2456043,"uid":158613,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T15:11:53.000Z","msg":"你的孩子在那兒？"},{"pid":"cd8af246331d6ffa8043a6a25f0a0c1aa208dd60","tid":2456043,"uid":23815,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T15:12:49.000Z","msg":"你當以家學校課程好好撚得閒呀 ？ <br />\n屌你老母楊潤狗"},{"pid":"e5bf9d05b779761cdf276fc1737a22bc588e08c9","tid":2456043,"uid":256286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,